OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a cloudy morning
OL,6,Fwith scattered showers. It will turn
OL,7,Fgenerally drier and brighter in the
OL,8,Fafternoon with some hazy sunshine, but
OL,9,Fstill the chance of the odd shower.
OL,10,FWarm.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will be mostly dry and
OL,13,Fcloudy through the evening and
OL,14,Fovernight but with the chance of the
OL,15,Fodd shower.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FA largely dry start but
OL,18,Frather cloudy. Scattered showers will
OL,19,Fdevelop through the day, these heavy
OL,20,Fand perhaps thundery at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
